emselves together in their cities throughout all the provinces of the king Ahasuerus, to lay hand on such as sought their hurt: and no man could withstand them; for the fear of them fell upon all people.","year":-452},{"id":"recLMLRs18C87K5Uh","ref":"Esth.9.3","text":"And all the rulers of the provinces, and the lieutenants, and the deputies, and officers of the king, helped the Jews; because the fear of Mordecai fell upon them.","year":-452},{"id":"recI1yLhpKKZJDv2j","ref":"Esth.9.4","text":"For Mordecai was great in the king’s house, and his fame went out throughout all the provinces: for this man Mordecai waxed greater and greater.","year":-452},{"id":"reccZVffZeSek68f2","ref":"Esth.9.5","text":"Thus the Jews smote all their enemies with the stroke of the sword, and slaughter, and destruction, and did what they would unto those that hated them.","year":-452},{"id":"recaL0KjT0VSItqlx","ref":"Esth.9.6","text":"And in Shushan the palace the Jews slew and destroyed five hundred men.","year":-452},{"id":"recz1fsbYg9IrWUtl","ref":"Esth.9.7","text":"And Parshandatha, and Dalphon, and Aspatha,","year":-452},{"id":"recviaxaOtuYvhZmV","ref":"Esth.9.8","text":"And Poratha, and Adalia, and Aridatha,","year":-452}]}
